name: Intermutual Group
overview:
Intermutual Partner’s efficacy, market influence and combination of the old school pounding the payment and new school technology allows deep penetration into a multitude of various online and offline industries. IMP targets undeserved markets and builds revenue generating models into segmented sales or service based organizations. The IMP proprietary value creation process renders an in depth perspective to both the evolutionary portion of the business and the potential scalability of the current offering. Our team of result driven analysts provide out of the box experience and objective based systematic approaches to early capital adoption and successful launch strategies.

The IMP model is based upon years of entrepreneurial prowess. Our management team comes to the table with diverse backgrounds and proven track records of successful launches in growth industries. With a multi generational perspective and demonstrated approach our team identifies a fast track method of building or reconstructing the companies frame work from floor to ceiling. The company’s team and model is then vetted against in house resources developing business prototypes and formulating speculative go to market protocols. Our model employs methodology and research that teaches, mentors and creates corporate evolution.
